message.body: Word of the day is confidence. How are the knees?
Not terrible. One of them is a bit bruised but it feels pretty okay
Well, I stunk again. But I didn't fall down this time at least :-)
Takes more stones than I have to go compete. So, well done! There is nothing wrong with stinking at a national level.
Any more days of competition, or can you now sit back and just watch?
No, three games yesterday and six today, I'm done now
Might go check out a Reno Aces game tonight, they have a AAA club here
With all this talk of Reno, I'm tempted to go for the air races in September.
It's dirt cheap to stay here during the week. The only annoying part is getting here - no direct flights.
With luck I can beg/borrow/steal a private pilot with a plane out there.
